>>a, they won't die.  B, shame beats cash.

>>we don't --

>>No, but that's the point.  That's why you make the transition.  I mean,
>>read the life of Malcolm X.  I mean, it's -- one morning people say -- I
>>mean, this is what Adam Smith meant when he talked about the man in the
>>mirror in the theory of moral sentiments.  Inside all of us, except the
