http://www.conservative.org:80/free/ST94/Excess94.html 204.71.237.88 19970208144320 text/html 7185
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Saturday, 08-Feb-97 14:44:07 GMT
Last-modified: Monday, 01-Jul-96 01:16:49 GMT
