http://www.conservative.org:80/wash_times/ed.2-26.html 204.71.237.88 19970208190503 text/html 4093
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Saturday, 08-Feb-97 19:05:49 GMT
Last-modified: Monday, 26-Feb-96 05:56:14 GMT
Content-length: 3908
