wouldn't be able to do it.  They'd spill gas all over.  There'd be a fire
hazard.  I mean, go back and read them sometime.  Trusting in people,
sharing information, broadening out the base of everybody having a chance
to play is very, very important.  Now, really radical idea, probably get in
trouble again, but I can't help --
