<DOCHDR>
http://www.conservative.org:80/free/ST93/Species93.html 204.71.237.88 19970208144730 text/html 7450
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Saturday, 08-Feb-97 14:48:10 GMT
Last-modified: Monday, 01-Jul-96 01:13:29 GMT
