http://www.conservative.org:80/pff/renew/trans1095.html 204.71.237.88 19970209114525 text/html 100953
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Sunday, 09-Feb-97 11:46:04 GMT
