<TITLE> The Index of Economic 
Freedom </TITLE>
<H2> <CENTER>The Index of Economic Freedom 
</H2>

<BR>


<BR>
<H3>By <a href="/heritage/staff/johnson.htm">Bryan T. Johnson</a><BR>
and<BR>
Thomas P. Sheehy</H3>



<BR>

<B>The Heritage Foundation<BR>
214 Massachusetts Avenue, N.E.<BR>
Washington, D.C. 20002<BR>
202-546-4400<BR></B></CENTER>
<BR>

<P><B>Bryan T. Johnson</B> is a Policy Analyst at The Heritage Foundation.<BR>
<B>Thomas P. Sheehy</B> is the Jay Kingham Fellow in International Regulatory Affairs at 
The Heritage Foundation.
