Reports.   
 <P> [5]This method allowed the authors to generate an average income level for nearly all countries,   
since    
these figures are readily available.   
 <P>[6] For each country, the following sources were used unless otherwise noted: United Nations    
Development Project, <I>United Nations Human Development Report: 1994;</I>  International    
