Tables, 1993.</I>   
 <P>[7] GDP is used in most cases.  When only GNP figures were available, it is so stated.   
 <P>[8] World Bank, <I>World Development Report: 1993.</I>   
 <P>[9] For each country, the following sources were used unless otherwise noted: USTR, <I>1994    
